title: Dems Scramble in Pennsylvania
description: Fellas break down the Pennsylvania Senate debate and the ensuing media reaction before playing King of the Hill. Mike Lawler joins the progrum for a conversation about his campaign to defeat Dem Congressman Sean Patrick Maloney in New York.
author: hello@ruthlesspodcast.com (Mike Lawler, Michael Duncan, Josh Holmes, Comfortably Smug, John Ashbrook)
